==Useful Info==
'''Demonspawn corrupters''' are demonspawn summoners who can also inflict temporary [[corrosion]]. They can be found in the [[Pandemonium]].

{{monster spells}}

==History==
*Prior to [[0.28]], demonspawns with the corrupter class could have any base (monstrous, gelid, infernal, or torturous), instead of all of them being torturous. Also, corrupters could cast [[Corrupting Pulse]] instead of [[Entropic Weave]].
*Prior to [[0.19]], corrupters had [[Corrupt Body]] instead of [[Corrupting Pulse]].
*Corrupters were added in [[0.14]].

